OL,3,CDUP presses Chancellor for 'better
OL,4,Cfinancial settlement' for Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson said he has
OL,8,Fpressed the Chancellor for a better
OL,9,Ffinancial settlement for Northern
OL,10,FIreland.
OL,12,FHe said he also asked Rachel Reeves
OL,13,Ffor borrowing powers that would allow
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland to build more homes,
OL,15,Fimprove infrastructure and support
OL,16,Feconomic growth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
