FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779494576
OL,3,CDUP presses Chancellor for 'better
OL,4,Cfinancial settlement' for Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,FIt comes as the Stormont Executive
OL,8,Fremains unable to agree a new three-
OL,9,Fyear budget almost two months into the
OL,10,Fnew financial year as ministers
OL,11,Fcomplain their departments need more
OL,12,Ffunding.
OL,14,FMr Robinson said his party colleague,
OL,15,FEducation Minister Paul Givan is
OL,16,Ffacing a funding shortfall running
OL,17,Finto hundreds of millions of pounds,
OL,18,Fwhich could lead to teaching posts
OL,19,Flost, larger class sizes and reduced
OL,20,Fsupport for children with additional
OL,21,Fneeds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
