FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779494576
OL,3,CDUP presses Chancellor for 'better
OL,4,Cfinancial settlement' for Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,FIn an email to DUP party members, Mr
OL,8,FRobinson said he heard from business
OL,9,Fleaders this week that while Northern
OL,10,FIreland has huge potential, it is
OL,11,Fbeing held back by planning delays,
OL,12,Funderinvestment and systems that
OL,13,Fsimply do not work quickly enough.
OL,15,FHe described a "wider reality which
OL,16,Fcannot be ignored", that "Northern
OL,17,FIreland is being asked to deliver
OL,18,Ffirst-class public services with
OL,19,Fsecond-class funding".
OL,26,@wD@POUxD@RO]xD@ZOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779494576
OL,3,CDUP presses Chancellor for 'better
OL,4,Cfinancial settlement' for Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,FMr Robinson said people are feeling
OL,8,Fthe strain, from patients waiting
OL,9,Flonger than they should, local
OL,10,Fservices disappearing and
OL,11,Fdeteriorating roads.
OL,13,FHe said he has been making this case
OL,14,Fdirectly to Government.
OL,16,F"I met the Prime Minister and made it
OL,17,Fclear that Northern Ireland is part of
OL,18,Fthe United Kingdom and must be funded
OL,19,Ffairly as part of it.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779494576
OL,3,CDUP presses Chancellor for 'better
OL,4,Cfinancial settlement' for Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,F"A strong Union must mean a fair
OL,8,FUnion," he said.
OL,10,F"This week we again pressed the
OL,11,FChancellor for a better financial
OL,12,Fsettlement and for borrowing powers
OL,13,Fthat would allow Northern Ireland to
OL,14,Fbuild more homes, improve
OL,15,Finfrastructure and support economic
OL,16,Fgrowth."
OL,18,F"At the same time, Government must get
OL,19,Fits own house in order.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@GO]rD@AOUxD@HO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779494576
OL,3,CDUP presses Chancellor for 'better
OL,4,Cfinancial settlement' for Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,F"Around #350 million is lost every
OL,8,Fyear through fraud and error, while
OL,9,Finefficiency and unacceptable
OL,10,Fabsenteeism continue within parts of
OL,11,Fthe civil service."
OL,13,FHe went on: "Working families and
OL,14,Fbusinesses across Northern Ireland are
OL,15,Falready under enough pressure.
OL,17,F"They do not need new charges or
OL,18,Fstealth taxes from Stormont on top of
OL,19,Fcontinued Treasury underfunding.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@SO]uD@MOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779494576
OL,3,CDUP presses Chancellor for 'better
OL,4,Cfinancial settlement' for Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,F"Talent, hard work and potential,
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland has them in abundance.
OL,10,F"What has been missing for too long is
OL,11,Fgovernment willing to match that
OL,12,Fambition with proper investment."
OL,14,F"The UK Government has provided a
OL,15,F#19.3 billion per year on average
OL,16,Ffunding settlement for the Spending
OL,17,FReview period, the largest in real-
OL,18,Fterms in the history of devolution.
OL,20,F"It is the responsibility of the
OL,21,FExecutive to manage that carefully.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUtD@aO]vD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779494576
OL,3,CDUP presses Chancellor for 'better
OL,4,Cfinancial settlement' for Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,F"In addition to this, the Chancellor
OL,8,Fhas announced over #750 million
OL,9,Fadditional funding in Barnett
OL,10,FConsequentials."
OL,12,F"The Secretary of State is engaging
OL,13,Fregularly with the Minister for
OL,14,FFinance on the budget, and it is clear
OL,15,Fhe faces significant challenges in
OL,16,Fgetting agreement from the Executive,
OL,17,Fand has asked for additional funding
OL,18,Ffrom the Government.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@PO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
